  Description: The blood of the fey flows through your veins, saturating you with
    their magic and making you truly one of them. You gain the fey trait, in addition
    to the gnome and humanoid traits. Choose one cantrip from the primal spell list.
    You can cast this spell as a primal innate spell at will. A cantrip is heightened
    to a spell rank equal to half your level rounded up. You can change this cantrip
    to a different one from the same list once per day by meditating to realign yourself
    with the First World; this is a 10-minute activity that has the concentrate trait.
